Detailed Description

cvmx_sso_wq_int_cnt#

CSR reserved addresses: (64): 0x7200..0x73f8 CSR align addresses: =========================================================================================================== SSO_WQ_INT_CNTX = SSO Work Queue Interrupt Count Register (one per group)

Contains a read-only copy of the counts used to trigger work queue interrupts. For more information regarding this register, see the interrupt section.
